OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FFire chiefs have argued that urgent
OL,7,Finvestment in fire services is needed
OL,8,Fafter figures revealed crews in
OL,9,FEngland tackled at least 26,902
OL,10,Fwildfires in 2025.
OL,12,FServices responded to at least 12,454
OL,13,Fgrassland, woodland or crop fires
OL,14,Fbetween March and May 2025 - more than
OL,15,Ffour times the number recorded in 2024
OL,16,Fand the highest spring total in more
OL,17,Fthan a decade.
