OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FTen fire services faced record numbers
OL,7,Fof wildfires in springtime as dry
OL,8,Fweather created drought conditions in
OL,9,Fseveral parts of the country.
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Fire Rescue Service
OL,12,Fand Tyne and Wear Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService both responded to 1,000 more
OL,14,Ffires in the spring months this year
OL,15,Fthan the same period in 2024.
OL,17,FThe figures revealed came from 35 of
OL,18,Fthe 43 mainland fire services in
OL,19,FEngland, meaning the actual number of
OL,20,Fwildfires in the country will be
OL,21,Fhigher.
