OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FAndy Cole, Chief Fire Officer for
OL,7,FDorset and Wiltshire Fire Service,
OL,8,Fsaid this summer was "one of the most
OL,9,Fchallenging for wildfires that we've
OL,10,Fever faced".
OL,12,F"Our firefighters worked around the
OL,13,Fclock in arduous conditions, often for
OL,14,Fdays at a time, to protect lives,
OL,15,Fhomes, and our natural environment,"
OL,16,FMr Cole said.
OL,18,FHe added that the increased frequency
OL,19,Fand intensity of wildfires also put "a
OL,20,Fstrain on resources, such as equipment
OL,21,Fand finances".
