OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FThe National Fire Chiefs Council
OL,7,Fpraised firefighters who "worked
OL,8,Ftirelessly and under extreme
OL,9,Fconditions" to keep the public safe,
OL,10,Fbut said urgent and long-term
OL,11,Finvestment was needed to support fire
OL,12,Fservices to cope with the costs
OL,13,Frelated to wildfires.
OL,15,FA spokesperson from the Ministry of
OL,16,FHousing, Communities and Local
OL,17,FGovernment - the department
OL,18,Fresponsible for fire service funding -
OL,19,Fsaid they are taking decisive action
OL,20,Fto help fire services.
