OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FThey said this included a #70 million
OL,7,Fboost to standalone fire and rescue
OL,8,Fauthorities in 2026 and funding a
OL,9,FNational Resilience Wildfire Advisor
OL,10,Fto support a more coordinated response
OL,11,Fto wildfires.
OL,13,FWhy were there so many wildfires in
OL,14,F2025?
OL,16,FAccording to the National Fire Chiefs
OL,17,FCouncil, the increase in wildfires was
OL,18,Fresult of changing weather in the UK.
