OL,3,CWhy were there so many wildfires this
OL,4,Cyear?
OL,6,FMost wildfires in the UK are the
OL,7,Fresult of human activity - such as
OL,8,Ffrom barbecues or deliberate arson -
OL,9,Fbut the National Fire Chiefs Council
OL,10,Fsaid higher temperatures mean they
OL,11,Fstart earlier in the year and last
OL,12,Flonger.
OL,14,FThe effects on wildlife can be
OL,15,Fdevastating, with experts estimating
OL,16,Fthat recovery of landscapes can take
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
